#, no-wrap
#~ msgid "Shared clipboard"
#~ msgstr "Porta-retalls compartit"

#, no-wrap
#~ msgid "<div class=\"caution\">\n"
#~ msgstr "<div class=\"caution\">\n"

#, no-wrap
#~ msgid ""
#~ "<p>The shared clipboard of *GNOME Boxes*\n"
#~ "is enabled by default. This can allow sensitive data to be copied by\n"
#~ "mistake from the virtual machine onto the host operating system or vice\n"
#~ "versa.</p>\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<p>El porta-retalls compartit de les *Màquines de GNOME*\n"
#~ "està habilitat per defecte. Això pot permetre que les dades sensibles siguin copiades\n"
#~ "per error de la màquina virtual al sistema operatiu amfitrió o\n"
#~ "viceversa.</p>\n"

#, no-wrap
#~ msgid "<p>We recommend you to disable the shared clipboard.</p>\n"
#~ msgstr "<p>Us recomanem que desactiveu el porta-retalls compartit.</p>\n"

#~ msgid "To disable the shared clipboard:"
